# Project core — layered backend

- Source of truth: [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) and [docs/architecture-and-layers.md](docs/architecture-and-layers.md).
- Fixed folders: **`infraestructure`** (with "e"), **`configuration`** (singular) — do not rename to "infrastructure" / "configurations".
- **Domain** must not import **Infraestructure** (no Mongoose, `IM*`, concrete Kafka in domain).
- Repository contracts in domain (`I*RepositoryRead` / `I*RepositoryWrite`); implementations in `src/infraestructure/repository/<context>/`.
- Composition and DI in `src/configuration/factory/`.
- Tests in `src/__tests__/`; coverage target ≥ 80% (`yarn test:coverage` in AGENTS.md).
- Endpoints: when changing routes/contracts, update [src/contracts/service.yaml](src/contracts/service.yaml).
- **Business rules** belong **mandatorily** in **Service** (`src/domain/<context>/service/`); never in Repository or Controller. See [rule.business-rules-layers.mdc](rule.business-rules-layers.mdc).
